### Manual (Vercel)

1. Set `DATABASE_URL` in Vercel → Project Settings → Environment Variables
2. Re-deploy (`git push`)
3. Visit the deployed URL — home dashboard should load with 0 errors
4. Add an expense via `/add`, verify it appears on `/expenses`
5. Edit and delete the expense — confirm no 500 errors
